[Guest]: There was a forum called usenet a bunch of forums called usenet. This is around the 1990s and a little earlier than that

00:10:23.020 --> 00:10:23.900
[Guest]: and

00:10:23.900 --> 00:10:28.140
[Guest]: The general pattern was that there were a bunch of people out there who were familiar who knew had a certain

00:10:28.540 --> 00:10:32.300
[Guest]: General code of how to communicate and talk to each other every so often in the year

00:10:32.700 --> 00:10:37.100
[Guest]: There would be a new influx of users a periodic influx from a bunch of colleges where people came there

00:10:37.260 --> 00:10:40.300
[Guest]: They now had access to usenet and they would come in

00:10:41.020 --> 00:10:45.840
[Guest]: And that was generally called and that was usually in september and that period would be a period of adjustment

00:10:46.380 --> 00:10:51.740
[Guest]: They would have to the new users would end up learning and imbibing the general rules of and code of conduct online

00:10:51.740 --> 00:10:54.780
