00:11:24.780 --> 00:11:27.420
[Guest]: But it's not it was more like understanding how to talk to each other

00:11:28.140 --> 00:11:36.060
[Guest]: And that was termed eternal september. That's a fantastic term and it's like we're still in an eternal september. Yes, it is

